lways afraid that i waited too long then afterward wonder if it was too soon i have had to have many of my dogs euthanized to i am watching mine as you are watching yours i will shed some tears for yours as i grieve for mine Shaggy dog story EastEnders One Tree Hill (TV series) Atomic Kitten Episodes of Lost (Season 1) Avenue Q Similarities between the Bible and the Qur'an Time Out of Mind Futurama (TV series - season 5) RuneScape quests Theory of conduct Jon Secada The Inside Wild at Heart (Buffy episode) Sin City Humphrey Bogart Pitaten Care Bears Boom Crash Opera Knots Landing Babe Ruth Euthanasia Cindy Sheehan The Catcher in the Rye Friends Bon Jovi Kimi Finster The Amber Spyglass Cliff Richard Kodocha Waylon Jennings Darwin from Insectivorous plants to Worms 2000 Australian Grand Prix Buddy Guy Phoebe Halliwell The Shining (film) Current teachings of Prem Rawat Book of Isaiah W.I.T.C.H. About a Boy Dean Koontz John Lennon The Apprentice 2 The Death Gate Cycle Le Malade imaginaire Teacher's Pet (Disney) The Contender (television series) Havanese Miss Saigon Father's Day (Doctor Who) Sydney Riot of 1879 50 First Dates Main characters of Fullmetal Alchemist Series finale Mojave people Joseph (Hebrew Bible) Grief Non-Hodgkin's lymphoma Dog training The Grim Adventures of Billy and Mandy Piccolo Junior Saga Car handling AFI 100 Years series Billboard Hot 100 Patrick Star The Wizard of Oz (1939 film) Night (book) Immortality Phoebe Buffay's songs Prostate cancer John the Baptist Repentance Reservoir Dogs The Beatles discography Ty Cobb South Park Characters in the Smurfs Grandview, U.S.A. Kill Bill Singlish Pet skunk Trailer Park Boys Queen (band) Garfield Rent (musical) Battle of the Bulge Doug God Emperor of Dune Hip hop collaborations Montgomery Burns 1957 World Series Gothic metal Radiohead The Pet Sounds Sessions Drag racing 